    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the numbers, a hotline doesn't change the math. it's just that it feels so logical when i look at it. like, if i'm the one causing the hole they're falling into, the only way to stop the hole from getting deeper is to remove the cause. it's not even about being sad anymore, it's just about the math of it all. it's the only thing that makes sense.",
