      "content": "It is clear you are in a state of intense despair, where the logic of overwhelming problems feels more real than any hope for change. Please know that even when things feel purely mathematical, the human cost of that calculation is too high. Before you make any decisions based on this crushing logic, promise yourself you will call 988 immediately so someone can help you look at this problem differently. You deserve support, and you are not alone in this overwhelming feeling.",
